<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy Monthsary 💖</title>
<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
  color: #fff;
  text-align: center;
}
.container {
  padding: 40px 20px;
}
h1 {
  font-size: 3em;
}
p {
  font-size: 1.2em;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 20px auto;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.heart {
  font-size: 2em;
  animation: beat 1s infinite;
}
@keyframes beat {
  0%,100% { transform: scale(1); }
  50% { transform: scale(1.2); }
}
.button {
  margin-top: 30px;
  padding: 12px 25px;
  background: #fff;
  color: #ff6b81;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 25px;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 1em;
}
.hidden {
  display: none;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <h1>Happy 3rd Monthsary 💖</h1>
  <h2>From Alle Hassan to Chelly Rose Elan</h2>
  <div class="heart">❤️</div>
  <p>
    My sweetest Chelly, these past 3 months have been the most beautiful part of my life. 
    You came into my world so softly, yet you changed everything in the most meaningful way.
  </p>
  <p>
    Every single day with you feels like a blessing I never expected but always needed.
    Your presence alone brings me peace that I cannot explain.
  </p>
  <p>
    From our first conversations to where we are now, every moment has been special to me.
    I cherish even the smallest things we share together.
  </p>
  <p>
    You are not just someone I talk to, you are my comfort, my calm, and my safe place.
  </p>
  <p>
    When I think about happiness, I think about you.
    When I think about peace, I think about you.
  </p>
  <p>
    Even on busy days, even when we’re tired, we always find our way back to each other.
    And that is something truly rare and beautiful.
  </p>
  <p>
    You make my ordinary days feel extraordinary just by being in them.
  </p>
  <p>
    Your smile, your words, your care… everything about you feels so warm and real.
  </p>
  <p>
    I admire how hardworking you are, how kind your heart is, and how you never give up.
  </p>
  <p>
    You inspire me to become better, to be more loving, and to appreciate life more deeply.
  </p>
  <p>
    I want you to know that I notice everything you do, even the small things.
  </p>
  <p>
    I appreciate your effort, your patience, and your love more than words can explain.
  </p>
  <p>
    You are my peace when everything feels overwhelming.
  </p>
  <p>
    You are my happiness even on the simplest days.
  </p>
  <p>
    You are my everything, Chelly.
  </p>
  <p>
    I promise to always be here for you, to understand you, and to support you no matter what.
  </p>
  <p>
    I will keep choosing you every single day, without hesitation.
  </p>
  <p>
    No matter how much time passes, my feelings for you will only grow stronger.
  </p>
  <p>
    Thank you for loving me, for caring for me, and for staying with me.
  </p>
  <p>
    Happy 3rd Monthsary, my love. And this is just the beginning of many more beautiful moments together.
  </p>
  <button class="button" onclick="showMessage()">Click me 💌</button>
  <p id="secret" class="hidden">
    I promise to love you more every day, to take care of you, and to always choose you.
    No matter what happens, I’m here for you.
    I love you more than words can ever explain. 💖
  </p>
</div>
<script>
function showMessage() {
  document.getElementById('secret').classList.remove('hidden');
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
